@startuml activity-live-refresh-spine
'' PlantUML over Mermaid because this view emphasises WHICH layer owns each step (FS|Main|IPC|Renderer|
'' Stores|DOM swimlanes) and a kind-of branch with a converging "UI untouched" note; PlantUML activity
'' partitions render ownership + the decision diamond + a coloured note Mermaid flowcharts cannot lane.
'' Swimlane colours are literal palette hexes (tan #9F8766 FS, slate #3A5BA0 Main, amber #B1951D IPC,
'' teal #2D9574 Renderer, purple #A45BAD Stores, blue-violet/grey for DOM).
!include _vv-theme.iuml

title Live-refresh spine — layer ownership of one file-change → re-render

|#EEEBE8|Filesystem|
start
:editor writes file;
:chokidar watcher (retained path)\nfires "change"/"add"\nafter awaitWriteFinish (80ms);

|#E4E8F1|Main (Node)|
:kind-of path;
if (kind) then (image)
  :send vv:content {:path :kind}\n(no :text — binary);
else (markdown / text)
  :fs.readFileSync utf8;
  if (read ok?) then (yes)
    :send vv:content {:path :kind :text};
  else (throws)
    :send vv:error {:path :message};
    note right #FFCCCC: error path (red)
  endif
endif

|#F4F1E1|IPC seam|
:preload contextBridge\nwebContents.send → ipcRenderer.on;
:window.vv.onContent / onError;

|#E3F2ED|Renderer (re-frame)|
:rf/dispatch [:content/received] / [:content/error];
:event handler (PURE) builds tx\n(cond-> omit nil :doc/text; retract stale :doc/error);

|#EEE6EF|Stores|
:**:ds/transact** {:doc/path :doc/kind :doc/text :doc/open? :doc/order};
:bridge → [:ds/changed] → :ds/rev inc;
if (kind = markdown?) then (yes)
  |#E3F2ED|Renderer (re-frame)|
  :fx :markdown/render\n(async unified + SVG pipeline);
  :.then → [:content/rendered path stamp result];
  |#EEE6EF|Stores|
  :**:ds/transact** {:doc/path :doc/html :doc/toc :doc/assets};
elseif (kind = text?) then (yes)
  |#EEE6EF|Stores|
  :**:ds/transact** {:doc/html <pre vv-plain escaped>};
else (image)
  :no :doc/html\n(view renders <img file://> directly);
endif
:bridge → [:ds/changed] → :ds/rev inc\n(:doc/active sub recomputes);

|#E3E7F2|DOM|
:content-view Strategy picks the body by :doc/kind;
:markdown-body component-did-update\nset! innerHTML (:html result) (no VDOM diff);
floating note
  **UI untouched.** :ui/find ranges, scroll offset,
  :ui/theme, :ui/history all live in app-db and are
  never written by a :ds/* transaction — so the
  refresh leaves the reader exactly where they were.
end note
stop

legend right
  |= Colour |= Swimlane / concept |
  |<#9F8766>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;| Filesystem (editor + chokidar) |
  |<#3A5BA0>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;| Main process (Node IO) |
  |<#B1951D>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;| IPC seam (preload / contextBridge) |
  |<#2D9574>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;| Renderer (re-frame events + fx) |
  |<#A45BAD>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;| Stores (DataScript transactions) |
  |<#7590DB>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;| DOM (imperative innerHTML body) |
  |<#E0211D>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;| error path (vv:error) |
endlegend
@enduml
